  "blurb": "A landmark beachfront estate on the peaceful west coast of Koh Samui at Lipa Noi — eight bedrooms across landscaped grounds with 30 metres of beach frontage, a 22-metre infinity pool and an amazing view of the Five Islands. A wellness hub with a 371 m² gym, yoga lawn and tennis court, fully staffed with a private Thai chef. Among the island’s most sought-after villas for groups, weddings and events.",
  "detail": "A prime beachfront location on the peaceful, picturesque west coast of Samui makes this one of the island’s most sought-after luxury villas for group travel, weddings and private events. Set in its own landscaped estate of coconut palms and emerald lawns, it boasts a 30-metre beach frontage with a 22-metre infinity pool and an amazing view of the shimmering turquoise sea and the iconic Five Islands.\n\nSeparate pavilions set amidst manicured tropical gardens offer eight stylish bedrooms for up to sixteen guests, including children’s rooms with twin beds and an outdoor playground. Well-designed living and dining spaces include an air-conditioned media room with a Smart TV and movie projector, and a 20-seat dining room with a pair of swing beds. Around the pool, a breakfast room opens onto the beach, while a fully equipped show kitchen with a bar and a poolside sala create a convivial setting for sunset drinks and dining under the stars.\n\nThe villa’s world-class 371 m² gym is a standout for active travellers; a morning yoga and meditation session, or a massage on the beachfront lawn, leaves a lasting impression. Training sessions for yoga, meditation and Muay Thai can be arranged, with in-villa massage and spa appointments bookable at an extra fee, plus a tennis court on site. Fully staffed for five-star service, with an included private chef preparing exceptional Thai and international cuisine alongside vegetarian, vegan and children’s menus.",
